rip

public void rip()
         throws NoCDException,
                MusicIsRippedException,
                java.lang.Exception
Test, if a CD is inserted and if all tracks are ripped, rips the CD, downloads a cover, add the not ripped tracks to the main playlist.

Throws:
NoCDException - if no CD is inserted
MusicIsRippedException - if the music is already ripped
